===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[participant]] (fighter) in a [[boxing]] match.
# A [[breed]] of [[stocky]], [[medium-sized]], [[short-haired]] dog with a [[square-jawed]] [[muzzle]].
#The person running a game of [[two-up]].

